// Stubbed for PF1e: this lifecycle handler is inherited from pf2e and
// references stats (focus_points / hero_points / actions_remaining / etc.)
// that do not exist in PF1e character_stats.rpgs. PF1e either has no
// analogous event, or the event will be re-implemented in a later session.
// Stubbing to an empty sequence preserves the file's event registration so
// the system loader does not choke on a missing handler name.
mechanic reset_actions_on_combatant_added(event_names = "combatantAdded") =
  sequence(effects = []);
